{"tid":1634262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同你講今晚做乜都唔係問題","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:56:46.000Z","uid":40051,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c68094bc50d562ac819a8680a145c54c5265ab","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係目標清晰，目的清楚</span></span><br />\n覺得岩就推唔該！<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日都幫人大維修，大致上都維修曬。今晚大家如果要出去再裝修，想問下大家重有乜野裝修到？<br />\n無曬目標裝修，係街度鳩fing? 裝修唔係問題，要有目的同目標。目的大家都有，但目標都裝修得七七八八，大家要再次諗翻下一步應該做乜，而唔係長期裝修。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有post話今晚唱歌都唔係問題，但可唔可以幫手順便做文宣啊，唔好淨係唱歌。行多一步就多好多。<br />\n<br />\n最後，休唔休息呢一個問題都好重要，但你休唔休息都唔再係連登話事，因為18區各有各決定，咁先係做到遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁，希望大家再唔好再失焦同比5毛帶風向。先討論，後實施，再檢討。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"a1f7171678373e41cd3126f9fcc9f1bbb5ad413f","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b0f1f7ba4063dfea4af7b16781e4f0474b7a151","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e784b1e361cfc824b167c0203e63eb2eb97f160c","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30b0701ad4bb223399a54a69aefcb5bfcf75fcea","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"139a2603ad72623f61087b1e5e82f15d676d0a1a","tid":1634262,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"618e805f920fb73eff488e6eceedefcab05b6547","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cea070c380f3320f599cddd0d37af343817b509","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"e70a7ef064ea31a9fd4b238edd3e90d336f579bc","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"968f3650727870bba4818b18153e7cf62d864efe","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fdb966ddc7b57901dd95bf3bb91063ce4bf0ed1","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"無人推"},{"pid":"066a7c11c6d2b047dfe68254f16a75f8cb24724d","tid":1634262,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb775152339d4326b1fe8de2e0c8dc0ede87b119","tid":1634262,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73b0fd965356d89001dd09421a349f50da9b3010","tid":1634262,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"議員辦事處好多未裝修<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵接近一半仲開到"},{"pid":"2e34cf0f9617c3d20b8e92455455aa1e227af4c2","tid":1634262,"uid":239086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"重陽節就應該集中追悼過咗身嘅義士先烈，唔好搞其他嘢，除非有人/狗主動攻擊。"},{"pid":"62786b82840cd42b48fa4b6202b2bfb44c10e8b5","tid":1634262,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"係 應該諗下之後除咗裝修仲有咩行動<br />\n裝修唔會日日都有得做 <br />\n嚟